---
title: Crumbed Tofu & Katsu Sauce with Garlic Rice & Soy Veggies
description: Tofu is a must-have ingredient in a veggie recipe, but that doesn’t mean you can’t have a little fun with it. Try crumbing the tofu in
panko breadcrumbs for a bit of crunch and texture. A dark katsu sauce drizzled on top and a bunch of veggies, you will never want
tofu and rice any other way.

